Entries.default: "You're welcome to enjoy the Court's offerings - and that's all. Eat, gamble, fall on your face drunk, but don't go snooping for trouble."
"Them doors are locked for a reason. So piss off, eh?"
"I said you can't go in there!"
"Guard the door to the command tower! Protect Captain Benweth at any cost!"
"Rattle them doors again, and I'll rattle you."
